.TH SOFTKMS 1 "February 2025" "softKMS 0.0.1" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
softkms \- Modern Software Key Management System CLI
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B softkms
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] \fICOMMAND\fR [\fIARGS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
softKMS is a secure, modern alternative to SoftHSM with HD wallet support,
written in Rust. It provides enterprise key management, hierarchical
deterministic (HD) wallets, and PKCS#11 compatibility.
.PP
The \fBsoftkms\fR command provides a CLI interface to interact with the
softKMS daemon for key management operations.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-s\fR, \fB\-\-server\fR \fIURL\fR
Server address (default: http://127.0.0.1:50051)
.TP
\fB\-p\fR, \fB\-\-passphrase\fR \fIPASSPHRASE\fR
Passphrase for keystore (if not provided, will prompt interactively)
.TP
\fB\-t\fR, \fB\-\-token\fR \fITOKEN\fR
Identity token for authentication (alternative to passphrase)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help information
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version information
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
\fBinit\fR
Initialize the keystore with a passphrase
.TP
\fBgenerate\fR
Generate a new key
.TP
\fBlist\fR
List all keys
.TP
\fBsign\fR
Sign data with a key
.TP
\fBverify\fR
Verify a signature
.TP
\fBdelete\fR
Delete a key
.TP
\fBimport\-seed\fR
Import a BIP39 seed phrase
.TP
\fBderive\fR
Derive a child key from a seed
.TP
\fBidentity\fR
Identity management commands
.TP
\fBexport\-ssh\fR
Export key to SSH format
.TP
\fBexport\-gpg\fR
Export key to GPG format
.SH EXAMPLES
Initialize the keystore:
.PP
.nf
.RS
softkms init
.RE
.fi
.PP
Generate a new Ed25519 key:
.PP
.nf
.RS
softkms generate \-\-algorithm ed25519 \-\-label mykey
.RE
.fi
.PP
Sign data with a key:
.PP
.nf
.RS
softkms sign \-\-label mykey \-\-data "Hello World"
.RE
.fi
.PP
List all keys:
.PP
.nf
.RS
softkms list
.RE
.fi
.SH FILES
.TP
\fI/etc/softkms/config.toml\fR
Configuration file
.TP
\fI/var/lib/softkms/\fR
Default data directory
.TP
\fI/var/log/softkms/\fR
Log directory
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR softkms-daemon (8),
.BR softkms-pkcs11 (7)
